	<h1 class="title">那个跟着邮局走的银行，为什么一下就能融资 451 个亿？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-15 08:02:03 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18940/medium/18940.jpg?1449820303" alt="" />			
	</div>
